#X text 31 16 We've seen other simpler envelope examples and all of them were possible with [adsr~] if you ignore one or more stages. Hence \, so you can just rely on it if you will. This example is a review of some of these examples. Below \, we have single decay envelope that can be triggered with a gate or impulse.;
